Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:31.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:33.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你还好吗，伙计？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You okay, bud?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你看电影时睡着了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You fell asleep during the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我本想让你接着睡的，你睡着时可爱极了，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was gonna let you sleep, you looked so cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:50.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但接着你哭了起来，这就不那么可爱了\N{\fnArial\fs48}but then you started crying, and that was less cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:51.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不，我很好\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不知道为什么我开始哭了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know why I was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我的梦并不算悲伤\N{\fnArial\fs48}My dream wasn't really sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:03.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，天，看看几点的...还有我的土豪金新表！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, gee, look at the time... and my classy new watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:05.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让我送你回家吧，伙计\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's get you home, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:08.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃，你没错过多少剧情\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw, you didn't miss much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}原来外星人抓奶牛\N{\fnArial\fs48}Turns out they were abducting cows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是为了它们的早餐麦片星球！\N{\fnArial\fs48}'cause they needed milk for their cereal planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:13.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:14.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你走之前，\N{\fnArial\fs48}before you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:16.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我能问你点问题吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:17.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:20.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}妈妈有没有跟你谈起过...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Did mom ever talk to you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}粉钻石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pink Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}有些事情\N{\fnArial\fs48}There were some things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:26.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你妈不那么愿意提起\N{\fnArial\fs48}your mom didn't like to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:28.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我从没有向她询问过细节\N{\fnArial\fs48}I never pressed her for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:29.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:33.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}罗丝和我谈论过很多重要的事情-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose and I talked about tons of important stuff --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:37.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}音乐，漫画，将脚伸进沙子里-\N{\fnArial\fs48}music, comic books, getting sand between your toes --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你懂的，个人感受\N{\fnArial\fs48}you know, feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们年轻时都犯过错\N{\fnArial\fs48}We both made a lot of mistakes when we were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我认为迪斯科会重新流行起来，她则发动了一场战争\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought disco was coming back, she started a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:46.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我认为她感觉\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think she felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:49.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她必须告诉我她的一切，但我告诉她，\N{\fnArial\fs48}she had to confess everything to me, but I told her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}“过去已经过去了”\N{\fnArial\fs48}"The past is the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:53.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}“重要的是现在的你”\N{\fnArial\fs48}All that matters to me is who you are now."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:58.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而且她是一个神奇的，友爱的人\N{\fnArial\fs48}And who she was, was an incredible, loving being.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:00.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}晚安，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}'Night, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:01.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}晚安，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}'Night, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我又回到了这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好吧，我猜我能看看周围的环境\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, I guess I can look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是哪？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这-这是...\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's -- what is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对不起，我待会会收拾的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry, I'll clean that up later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当你告诉我你的梦时，\N{\fnArial\fs48}When you told me about your dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:32.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我就觉得耳熟\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought it sounded familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:36.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就是这个-桥子\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's it -- the Palan-kwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}其实，这个读作“轿子”\N{\fnArial\fs48}Actually, it's pronounced "palan-keen."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是宝石人们！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's the Gems!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们肯定知道这是什么！\N{\fnArial\fs48}They've gotta know about this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:46.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿，你知道这是什么吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, do you know anything about this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，你应该知道真相，而真相是...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, you deserve to know the truth, and the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我完全不知道是什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have no idea what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我根本就没见过\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've never seen it before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让一下，紫晶，让我...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Excuse me, Amethyst. Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:04.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃...其实...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh... W-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这看起来像是\N{\fnArial\fs48}it appears to be an illustration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}某些日记中常见的幻想\N{\fnArial\fs48}in some kind of journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}算了吧，你知道我指的是什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我做梦梦到了这个！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I had a dream where I saw this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}康妮和我在想也许...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Connie and I were wondering if maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，为什么你和康妮不-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, why don't you and Connie --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:16.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们不能去！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}为什么不呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对啊，为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我以为从此你们会告诉我所有事情\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought you were going to tell me everything from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，史蒂文，我们-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, Steven, we--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这和粉钻有关吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Does this have something to do with Pink Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我已经知道妈妈打碎了她\N{\fnArial\fs48}I already know mom shattered her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}所以这个有什么不能告诉我？\N{\fnArial\fs48}so what is it about this that you can't tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}停下，你让珍珠非常难受\N{\fnArial\fs48}Please, you're making Pearl very upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不！是我非常难受！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No! I'm very upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们，不能，去\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}罗丝不想让你看到那个地方\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose never wanted you to see this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}罗丝想？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那我想做的呢？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What about what I want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我受够了所有人都对我撒谎!\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sick of everyone lying to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:54.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}罗丝是我的母亲！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose is my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:57.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}所有人里，不是我最应该知道真相吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Out of anyone, don't I deserve to know the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}现在不行\N{\fnArial\fs48}This isn't the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:02.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我，不，管！我想去那里！现在！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't care! I want to go there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:02.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我对不起，我-我不应把书带来的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sorry. I -- I shouldn't have brought the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不，你应该带来的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, you should have brought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}还好有些东西能提供信息\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's lucky something has some information
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}否则我不得不她们口中撬出来！\N{\fnArial\fs48}that I don't have to get out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}康妮，我得带走这本书\N{\fnArial\fs48}Connie, I need to borrow this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}可以，只是一定要小心使用\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我一周之内还得还回图书馆呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}I gotta return it to the library in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等，史蒂文，你要去-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait, Steven, where are you --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，别-别走啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你一定要相信我\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不明白，石榴\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't understand, Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}至少你一直对我是坦诚的\N{\fnArial\fs48}At least you're usually honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我真的很想这样，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I really want to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但如果我告诉你为什么你不能去，\N{\fnArial\fs48}but if I tell you why you shouldn't go,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你只会心头长草的\N{\fnArial\fs48}you'll only want to go more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}啊？！那现在我更想去了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?! Well, now I really want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我这张嘴啊～\N{\fnArial\fs48}I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你不能去，因为我不能跟着你\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't go because I can't go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}石榴，为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet, why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我...我害怕\N{\fnArial\fs48}I... I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我-我-我不能离她太近\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I-I can't get near her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}啊～“她”！，哪个她？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah, "her!" Her, who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:04:59.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃，干！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}现在草长了一米多高了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now I've made it more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，求求你\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}请留下来...就当是为了我吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just stay here... for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不会的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:14.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸，我需要你的帮助！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad, I need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一切正-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is everything o--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我在梦里看到了一个地方-而且是真实存在的-\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's this place I saw in a dream -- and it's real --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但宝石人们不愿意告诉我任何信息！\N{\fnArial\fs48}but the Gems won't tell me anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那里和粉钻石有关\N{\fnArial\fs48}It has something to do with Pink Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我知道你不想涉及到母亲的过去，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know you didn't want to get involved with mom's past,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但我想知道真相！\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I want to know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这难道一点都不重要吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Doesn't that matter at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这当然很重要！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:33.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让我看看\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么宝石人不愿意带你去？\N{\fnArial\fs48}And the Gems won't take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:39.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是的\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:42.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}刚好我知道个人会！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, I know a guy who will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么，宇宙一家要去韩国了\N{\fnArial\fs48}So the Universes are going to Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}谢谢搭我们过去，安迪叔叔！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you for the ride, Uncle Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:49.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}啊，这不算什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah, it's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:53.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}俗话说，家人要帮助家人...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Like they say, family helps family...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:56.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}寻找神秘的远古遗迹\N{\fnArial\fs48}find mysterious ancient artifacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这会非常重要\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's gonna be very serious work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}没时间闲逛\N{\fnArial\fs48}No time for fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:02.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不过，就没时间稍稍享受一下？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, isn't there time for a little fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:04.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}谢谢！蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Kamsahamnida! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:32.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}干嘛这么着急？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's the hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就是这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你确定？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You sure this is the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:40.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是的，虽然很难解释，但我能感觉到\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. It's hard to explain, but I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗯...这里还挺漂亮的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm, sure is pretty here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}所以有东西让你感觉熟悉吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So does any of this look familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文？喔，你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven? Whoa, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你又开始流泪了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我很好，咱们接着走\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm fine. Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}算了，一起休息下吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我觉得这座山真的影响了你\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think this mountain's really messing you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:56.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这只可能意味着我们在接近！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This can only mean we're getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}来吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这看起来很熟悉啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}This feels familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸，帮我翻过围栏\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad, help me jump the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，天，我们上吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, boy. We're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:16.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}喔，你老爸不能再像以前那样翻墙了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, your dad really can't jump fences like he used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸，看那个！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:21.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就是这里了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:24.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但这个不一样啊？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}But it's different?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}在我梦里，它完全损坏了，而且是粉色的\N{\fnArial\fs48}In my dream, it was all broken down and pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这个看起来很新\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's in perfect condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}也许它从做了喷漆？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Maybe it got a paint job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，小粉\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, Pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我对不起你，我实在对不起你\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我本来能做的更好的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I should have done more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}小黄说一切很快会结束的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yellow says it'll all be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我在想你是怎么认为的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I wonder what you would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是你的星球，毕竟\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is your planet, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}至少我是这么想的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I still think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，你认识她吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}喔，伙计！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我的梦-我是从她的眼里看到的\N{\fnArial\fs48}My dreams -- I was seeing through her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我流的是她的泪！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've been crying her tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你去那里做什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我感觉听到了什么人\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought I heard someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}别急，我能搞定\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry, I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我认为这里不止我们\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think we're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:16.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿！呃，今天天不错，不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey! Uh, nice day out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:18.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我-我没看到你，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I -- I didn't see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你...呃...你好？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's, uh... what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:22.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我的钻石，我发现了个土著人\N{\fnArial\fs48}My diamond, I've found a native.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，呃，对！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我就来自这里！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm from here, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:33.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}“你好”，陛下\N{\fnArial\fs48}Annyeonghaseyo, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:35.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}带他过来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸，不要！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}多有趣啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}How curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我很惊讶人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm impressed by humanity's ability
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}在野外生存的能力\N{\fnArial\fs48}to survive in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}多么奇怪的星球\N{\fnArial\fs48}What a strange planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:56.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}还有哪里，一个脆弱如人类的存在还活着\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where else would a being as fragile as a human live,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:09:01.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而强大如钻石的却已消逝？\N{\fnArial\fs48}while a being as powerful as a diamond perish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就是在这里...\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is where it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:08.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她被打碎的\N{\fnArial\fs48}where she was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你说完了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Were you close?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}很快了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Very.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}噢，我非常抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, I'm awfully sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:17.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我能理解想继续生活有多难\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know how hard it is to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当你失去你关心的人时\N{\fnArial\fs48}when you've lost someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我也失去了一个对我非常重要的人\N{\fnArial\fs48}I lost someone very important to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我每天都在思念她\N{\fnArial\fs48}I miss her every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}每时每刻都是\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I think about her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但，她并不会回来了\N{\fnArial\fs48}But she's never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这种感觉很难承受\N{\fnArial\fs48}That feeling can be so hard to be okay with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:41.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我很惊讶一个人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm surprised that a human being
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:44.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}能理解我的感受\N{\fnArial\fs48}is capable of understanding how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}真是羞愧啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你的星球孕育着一个致命武器\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's a geo-weapon incubating in your planet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}它将很快摧毁一切\N{\fnArial\fs48}that will destroy everything shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但，你不应承受这些，不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But you don't deserve that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:59.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}致命武器，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Geo-weapon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:02.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你知道，我真的不应该出现在这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know, I really shouldn't be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但我很高兴我来了，最，后，一，次\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I'm glad I came back one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:09.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我可以最后再挽救她一次遗产\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can save one last piece of her legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, yeah? Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:11.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那真是个巨大的胳膊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's a big arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}把我放下来，求求你了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Put me down, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦！喔！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}将我放下吧，陛下！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Put me down, your highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸，爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:38.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}停下！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，我-我对不起！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, I'm -- I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我“看到”你来了这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}I saw you come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我“看到”蓝钻石在地球上\N{\fnArial\fs48}I saw Blue Diamond on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我“看到”她见到我并找到了我们所有人\N{\fnArial\fs48}I saw her see me and find all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不能和你出现在这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}I couldn't be here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她抓走了我爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}She took my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这都是我的错，我本该听你的话的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's all my fault. - I should have listened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们该怎么办，石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are we gonna do, Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:12.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们要前往深空，我们要将他救回来\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're going to space. We're going to get him back.
